OL,3,CTributes to 'Karate Kid legend' Chad
OL,4,CMcQueen after his death aged 63
OL,6,FThe family of Chad McQueen, son of
OL,7,FHollywood legend Steve McQueen, have
OL,8,Fpaid tribute to the Karate Kid star
OL,9,Ffollowing his death aged 63.
OL,11,FIn a statement on Instagram, McQueen's
OL,12,Fwife Jeanie and his children Chase and
OL,13,FMadison described him as a "loving
OL,14,Ffather" and said he had a life "filled
OL,15,Fwith love and dedication".
OL,17,F"His passion for racing not only
OL,18,Fhighlighted his exceptional talent,
OL,19,Fbut also served as a way to honour his
OL,20,Ffather's legacy, a testament to the
OL,21,Fvalues instilled in him," they wrote.
