OL,6,FThey said they would "continue not
OL,7,Fonly his legacy but our grandfather's
OL,8,Fas well".
OL,10,FIn a separate Instagram post, Chase
OL,11,Fwrote: "Knowing you're now reunited
OL,12,Fwith your Dad and Sister brings me
OL,13,Fsome comfort. Until we ride again I
OL,14,Flove you."
OL,16,FMcQueen is also survived by his son
OL,17,Ffrom a former relationship, Steven R.
OL,18,FMcQueen ` an actor, who appeared in
OL,19,FThe Vampire Diaries.
