OL,6,FMcQueen followed in his father's
OL,7,Ffootsteps - both on screen and on the
OL,8,Fmotor racing circuit.
OL,10,FHe became well-known for his role as
OL,11,FDutch, the antagonist in 1984's The
OL,12,FKarate Kid and its sequel two years
OL,13,Flater.
OL,15,FHe also produced two documentaries
OL,16,Fabout his father: I Am Steve McQueen
OL,17,Fin 2014 and Steve McQueen: The Man &
OL,18,FLe Mans the following year.
