OL,4,CMcQueen after his death aged 63
OL,6,FBesides his acting career, he spent
OL,7,Fyears racing professionally, and
OL,8,Ffunded McQueen Racing in 2010, which
OL,9,Fhe ran with his children Chase and
OL,10,FMadison.
OL,12,FThey created custom cars and
OL,13,Fmotorcycles and worked with the movie
OL,14,Findustry.
OL,16,FJon Hurwitz, one of the creators of
OL,17,FCobra Kai, the Karate Kid revival that
OL,18,Fhas proven a hit on Netflix, paid
OL,19,Ftribute to McQueen.
