OL,6,FHe said he and his colleagues had met
OL,7,Fwith McQueen to discuss a return to
OL,8,Fthe series.
OL,10,FPosting on X, Hurwitz described
OL,11,FMcQueen as a "Karate Kid legend,"
OL,12,Fadding: "Unfortunately, Chad was
OL,13,Funable to join us when it came time to
OL,14,Fshoot. At the end of the day, it
OL,15,Fwasn't meant to be. But Dutch will
OL,16,Falways be remembered as a badass'
OL,17,Fbadass in the Miyagiverse. He kicked
OL,18,Fass."
